snippet.title: Official Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: The official Call of Duty®: Modern Warfare® 3 launch trailer. The best-selling franchise in Xbox 360® history is back. The definitive multiplayer experience returns bigger than ever. Special Ops co-op is reinvented with all-new survival mode. Follow #MW3 updates on Twitter via @fourzerotwo, and join us at Facebook.com/MW3.
